author: Hannah (Sensational Sidekick)
title: CVS: Free 8X10 Print + Free Same Day Pickup
text:
Need a last minute Valentine’s Day Gift?❤️ Through tomorrow only, CVS Photo is offering up a FREE 8×10 Photo Print ($3.99 value) whenever you use promo code VALENTINE at checkout. Even sweeter, you can opt for FREE same day in-store pickup at your local CVS store to save on shipping!

Use your free print to make your own photo canvas… (Thanks, Suzan & Bonnie!)
